headline: Phillips 66 Q4 Earnings Call Highlights
summary: Phillips 66 (NYSE:PSX) management used its fourth-quarter and full-year 2025 earnings call to highlight what CEO Mark Lashier described as “strong financial and operating results,” driven by higher refining utilization, record clean product yields, and continued momentum in Midstream volumes.
